quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  10,100,"Soni nganiyiŵa yanti mundu jwalijose ni kulupilila ikaŵeje kwa lisosa lya Allah, ni akuŵikaga ilagasyo yakunyalaya ku aŵala ŵangali lunda (lwakuchetelela ilosyo ya Allah)."
  10,101,"Jilani: “Nnole, ana ichichi yaili kumawunde ni petaka!” Nambo ilosyo kwisa soni akutetela nganaŵa akamuchisye ku ŵandu ŵangaakukulupilila."
  10,102,"Ana ŵanganyao akwembecheya (inepe) yangaŵaga (chonasiko) chakulandana nti chisawu moŵa ga aŵala ŵaŵapite paujo pao? Jilani: “Basi jembecheyani, chisimu none jwakwe ndinamwe mu akwembecheya.”"
  11,67,"Ni wakwembekenye aŵala ŵaŵalitesile lupuso n’gumilo (waipotesi), mwanti ŵachelelwe m’majumba mwao (ali awile) chitindiŵalile."
  11,68,"Gamba kuŵa nti chisawu ŵanganyao nganatamejemo. Manyililani yanti chisimu achina Samuda ŵankaaniile M’mbuje gwao, manyililani yanti chonasiko chakunaula chaliji kwa achina Samuda."
  11,69,"Soni chisimu chene Achimitenga Ŵetu (ŵachilaika) ŵam’bichilile Ibrahima ni abali jakusengwasya. Ŵanganyao ŵatite: “Ntendele!” Jwalakwe jwatite (pakwanga): “Ntendele!” Basi jwalakwe nganijutamilisya nambo (mwachitemachitema) jwaiche nako kang’ombe kejoche."
  12,28,"Basi ndema jaŵajiweni kansu jakwe kuti jipapulidwe chakunyuma ŵatite: “Chisimu yalakweyi ni itagu yenu (jenumanja achimmasyeto), chisimu itagu yenu ili yekulungwa nnope.”"
  12,29,"“Yusufu! Ikwanjilani yalakweyi. Sano mmwe (ŵankwangu)! Ŵendani chikululuko pa sambi syenu, chisimu mmwe n’di mwa ŵandu ŵakulemwa.”"
  12,30,"Sano achimmasyeto ŵa mu nsinda ŵatite: “Ŵankwao ŵakuchimbichika (anduna) akunnyenga nchanda jwao jwalakwe akakusaka, chisimu chisako chagumbele nnope, chisimu uwwe tukwaona kuti ali nkusoya kwa kuonechela.”"